Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:29.19,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:24107,29196}{\blur3}On the stage, with the lights off…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:35.41,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:30656,35410}{\blur3}…blue shadows emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:41.95,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:37746,41959}{\blur3}Dancing 'round to hear the applause…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:49.21,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:42626,49216}{\blur3}…I listen carefully to an unpredictable tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:54.63,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49841,54638}{\blur3}Everyone has a dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:01:01.10,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56265,61102}{\blur3}…with stars in their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:07.65,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63355,67651}{\blur3}Stage light: a moment to shine…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:14.82,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:68277,74825}{\blur3}…this city becomes a shining star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:31.09,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:76285,91091}{\blur3}The flower in my heart\Nis as fragile as glass, a shinin' dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:37.55,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:91633,97556}{\blur3}You can do it if you want to,\Nso hold on tight to love…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:44.39,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:98140,104396}{\blur3}…because there's someone that smiles\Non the other side of my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:49.98,Opening alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:104562,109985}{\blur3}You can do it if you want to,\Nthis feeling in my heart…
