Comment: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:00.12,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:120120,120120}Main
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:06.54,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121079,126543}Kitajima Maya's talent was discovered\Nby a renown former actress, Chigusa Tsukikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:10.50,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126543,130505}…and now she has become\Na student of Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:15.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:130505,135427}After her performance at the first play,\Nin which she played one of the main roles…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:135427,140140}…purple roses were delivered\Nfrom an anonymous fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:27.10,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141183,147105}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(400,0)}—Episode 03—\NThe Beautiful Rival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150692,152694}{\i1}I wonder who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159409,161119}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165290,168960}A purple rose.\NDo you like it, Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168960,170128}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177636,179596}{\i1}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179596,182224}{\i1}I'm afraid of what she will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182224,184851}Ayumi, your tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186853,189272}Oh, what a strange child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189272,192192}She hasn't spoken since\Nwe came back from the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192192,194611}Ayumi, we all are finally together as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194611,196238}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196238,197864}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198990,202619}No sugar for mama\Nbecause she's on a diet for her next play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202619,203537}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203537,206873}No sugar for papa as well\Nbecause you're on a diet for your tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206873,207791}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207791,208750}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213588,217509}{\i1}She is coming closer and closer to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218427,220220}{\i1}…but just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220220,222220}{\i1}I won't let her become better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.39,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:223472,227393}The Crimson Goddess
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:227393,231356}Secret Relationship With Aoyagi Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.48,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:231356,233483}Inexperienced Actors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233859,236111}Great job, Masumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236111,238196}Every critic gave terrible reviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238196,240866}It's scary once Metropolitan Entertainment\Nputs an eye on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240866,241616}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241616,244661}You can buy all the major critics\Nto write what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247247,250834}What's wrong?\NYou feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250834,254254}Once I start something,\NI pursue whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259301,261470}That's what I learned from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.84,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:262846,264848}Tsukikage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265348,267851}What a terrible article!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267851,270479}Aoyagi is my patron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270479,273023}What kind of wording was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273023,276860}And that criticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276860,279404}I can see that it was only written\Nwith terrible intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283825,288914}Can you believe it?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288914,289748}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289748,290540}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290540,292417}What was the article about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292417,294127}Don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294127,296296}Someone was behind all the articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297672,302093}Someone who wants\Nto destroy Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302093,303386}But, Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303386,303887}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303887,305347}Look how it was written!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305347,309893}Don't mind the lying critics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309893,311269}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312187,313021}Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313021,314231}– Teacher!\N– Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314231,315816}– Hang in there!\N– Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315816,317442}Call Mr. Genzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317442,319694}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324741,328286}I had no idea she had heart problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330247,332207}What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335919,339798}But I was shocked by the critics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349057,351059}{\i1}Critics…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351059,353895}{\i1}I never thought of drama like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357774,359860}Stop chatting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359860,361695}We have to start practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362571,363405}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363405,364781}I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364781,366032}Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366032,367659}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367659,368034}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368034,369244}– Let me go.\N– Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369244,369870}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369870,370871}Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370871,371830}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371830,372539}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372539,374124}You terrible girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374124,377252}Running away from home,\Ndo you know how worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378335,379296}Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379296,380630}No, I won't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380630,381965}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381965,384801}I'll take you home\Neven with a leash on your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384801,385385}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385385,385927}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387846,388847}Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388847,389514}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389514,390431}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390431,391182}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391182,392225}Right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392225,393226}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393226,393935}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393935,395228}Sorry, Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395228,398690}…but I want to play, whatever it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398690,401151}What are you dreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401151,404321}You are being deceived with kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404321,405697}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405697,407991}I'm Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407991,409034}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409034,411453}You're the one who talked her into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412746,413955}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413955,415707}Give me my daughter back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419961,421004}Stop it, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421004,421880}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421880,423381}We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423381,425133}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426051,427093}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427093,433141}You have to choose if you want to go home\Nor stay here and study drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433141,435268}I want to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435268,437020}I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437020,439439}What are you talking about?!\NYou're not good at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439439,442943}There is no way you can be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442943,444486}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446488,450116}I can't let her go back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450116,452786}You're a mother,\Nsupposed to encourage your child…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452786,457165}…but all you do is tell she's not worth anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457165,459626}…and don't even listen to her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459626,460543}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460543,463713}Why don't you believe in her possibilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463713,466841}Why not invest in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466841,469177}Even if she's not good at anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469177,474307}…I can look at one possibility\Nshe has and expand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476351,478436}Listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478436,480563}What in the world do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480563,482774}You're not even a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484317,487404}To raise a child is not an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487404,492158}You don't know what I went through\Nraising her as a single mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492158,493326}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493326,495578}I'm taking my daughter home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495578,497998}If you don't move,\NI'll splash this boiling water on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497998,499290}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499290,500792}You can talk all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500792,502794}But when it comes down to it,\Nyou'll just protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502794,504045}Now, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504045,505171}I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506006,507173}I won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508550,509634}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511386,513138}…stupid daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526526,529529}The face of an actress is her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529529,534284}If the boiling water gets on her and she gets\Na scar, her career as an actress will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534284,535493}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535493,536369}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536369,538288}But I want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538288,540707}I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545378,546772}Do as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546772,548214}You are not my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548214,549883}You are no child of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549883,553094}No, you are not my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553094,555079}You are not my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555079,557223}Don't ever come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557223,560769}Never come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560769,562353}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564481,566483}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569736,570987}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576659,577744}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577744,580371}There's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584709,587377}These are old masks from mask acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588713,590507}Crying mask…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590507,592092}Laughing mask…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592092,594218}Angry mask…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594844,596429}Jealousy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596429,597472}Mercy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597472,598264}Struggle…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598264,599140}Pleasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599140,600266}Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604562,608733}An actress has to wear countless masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610318,612445}Remember, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612445,617575}Each of your experiences\Ngo directly towards acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617575,618618}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618618,619619}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619619,621454}You have a thousand masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621454,623039}A thousand masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626291,627919}A thousand masks…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630171,631381}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632715,634384}A thousand masks…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636594,637846}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637846,638888}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638888,639930}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645311,648648}I don't know what will happen\Nafter the next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648648,651484}She should be hospitalized\Nand treated thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654112,656197}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664330,665623}Genzo…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666166,668293}Oh, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668293,671129}Tell my students not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671129,673298}Yes, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673298,675383}What did the doctor say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675383,678678}He suggested that since\Nyou've been working too hard lately…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678678,681639}…you should be hospitalized and treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681639,685810}And that he wouldn't know\Nwhat will happen after the next attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685810,687562}Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688521,690773}You know it all too well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690773,695695}…I don't have the time nor the money\Nto be hospitalized right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695695,696738}Genzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698615,699781}Yes, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700950,709083}You are the only one who came with me\Neven after I lost all my wealth and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709083,710543}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710543,712837}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712837,714297}Twenty years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720178,722764}…when the light fell…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722764,727936}…and ruined my face so badly\Nthat even surgery couldn't fix it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727936,730230}…my acting career was over for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731897,739530}Your "Crimson Goddess" had such beauty\Nthat the audience will never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739530,747372}It's only natural that Director Ozaki Ichiren\Ngave you the play rights for it and no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759175,762804}Here, you should get some rest, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772605,774023}Teacher, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775817,776859}Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781739,782365}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784409,785118}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785118,786202}Hurry up and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786202,787870}We're about to start practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787870,788788}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792041,795752}I want to produce\N"The Crimson Goddess" somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801801,803759}In the name of Metropolitan Entertainment…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808099,809934}…we'll get it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809934,810977}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811769,816899}Tsukikage is about to train an actress\Nwho can play "The Crimson Goddess" herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820527,827535}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i·sa·a·i·u·e·o!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827535,831831}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i·sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831831,833833}Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833833,834667}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834667,836711}Your voice is the weakest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836711,839130}Stand against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839130,841632}The voice comes from the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845011,849390}Here, use your muscle and push this hand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853978,857899}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857899,858983}Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861151,865615}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865615,867283}More!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867283,872163}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i·sa·a…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.62,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:872163,874624}Madame White Rose Press Conference
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877877,879962}We're looking forward\Nto you both playing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879962,882298}Ms. Ayumi, what's your goal for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882298,885593}Do you want to be an actress like your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885593,889430}No. I will not be an actress like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895144,897563}She is my mother,\Nbut she's a rival as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897563,900441}I want to become a better actress\Nthan my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900441,901984}So the climax of "Miss White Rose"…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901984,904821}…can be expected to be a competition\Nbetween mother and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908866,910493}Madame, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913704,921504}{\i1}Hello. I'm terribly sorry for my horrible scene\Nover Maya the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921504,927218}{\i1}After I thought about it, now I understand that\NI should let her do as she wills, just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927218,929554}{\i1}It may be lonely or hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929554,935017}{\i1}…but I should at least let her do what\Nshe wants to do. It's the least that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935017,937937}{\i1}Please take care of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939188,941690}Here, let's burn the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941690,943109}Madame…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943109,944318}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944318,945236}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945236,948781}What she needs now\Nis separation from her past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948781,950867}Not to have anywhere to turn back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950867,951909}Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956204,957623}Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957623,960501}We are going to practice\Nusing the hall on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960501,961794}Using the hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961794,963921}I wonder what we will play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963921,966174}It's the first time to use the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966174,967300}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970094,972430}These are the words for this play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972430,973473}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973473,976099}Using those four words, I want you to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976099,976767}"Yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976767,977560}"No".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977560,978394}"Thank you".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978394,979937}"I'm sorry"…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985651,989864}You are not allowed to use any other words\Nexcept for those four words. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989864,990906}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990906,994744}The play will be improvised from my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994744,998164}You'll fail if your act or the words are not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998164,1000291}The next person will take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007131,1008841}Rei, get up on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008841,1010175}Uh… yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016599,1019602}Oh, aren't you Aoki Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019602,1022730}You've grown so much since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022730,1024397}Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024397,1025233}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025233,1027777}I haven't seen him for a while,\Nbut has your father been okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027777,1029028}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029028,1030738}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030738,1033658}It's about how you respond to her words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035284,1041832}Depending on her lines, you have\Nto use the same words, but different tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041832,1046002}Depending on your emotions and how you say it,\Nthe same words can be used so differently…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046629,1048172}There's something on your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048172,1048798}Eh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048798,1050007}Fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050007,1050800}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051300,1052760}Looks tough…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055137,1056639}Ms. Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062979,1064981}Miss Tsukikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064981,1067984}I'm Himekawa Ayumi from Ondine Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067984,1070987}May I please audit the lesson today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070987,1071946}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071946,1075408}You are learning acting too,\Nof course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075408,1080663}Miss Tsukikage, how about letting me\Nbe on the stage in place of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080663,1082957}I would like to practice with one of you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086127,1088254}She's about to test us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088254,1089297}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089297,1092216}But just with one student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092633,1093467}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093467,1094427}{\i1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094427,1096137}Get on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103686,1106022}Here, Maya, get on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114155,1115072}Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120369,1121871}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121871,1123539}…you dropped your pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123539,1125124}Uh… Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125124,1127585}What a nice pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127585,1128711}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128711,1131380}Do you have some time now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131380,1132590}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132590,1133758}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133758,1135384}Could you come by for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135384,1137011}This is my place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137011,1137887}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137887,1139263}Have a seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139263,1140514}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143768,1145686}Would you like coffee or tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146854,1148898}Which one would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153903,1154486}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154486,1155446}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155446,1157198}You don't like neither?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157198,1158366}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158366,1159575}Good job, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159575,1160451}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160451,1162286}Here, have some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162286,1163079}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163079,1164664}How much sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164664,1165790}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165790,1166707}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166707,1168376}You don't want sugar either?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168376,1170086}Man, that girl's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170086,1172838}But Maya is doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183015,1185101}Wow, it's been an hour now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187269,1189438}{\i1}I didn't think she could do this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189438,1192024}{\i1}But watch, it'll soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193401,1195069}I want to play some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195069,1196487}What kind of music do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202702,1203619}It's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203619,1204495}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204495,1206163}Tell me what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229770,1232982}Using four words,\Nthere's no way she can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232982,1234984}{\i1}I wonder what she's about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247163,1248038}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252960,1255004}There, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258507,1259759}She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260843,1262762}– Great job.\N– I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264305,1265806}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268768,1270477}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276150,1279610}{\i1}This is the first time\Nthat someone could beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282156,1284033}{\i1}Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284909,1287703}{\i1}Someday we might compete on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288913,1290998}Really, Ayumi did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290998,1293375}Yes, suddenly.\NI was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293375,1296378}But it's good to see that you are doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296378,1297004}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297004,1300090}I heard there was a lot of commotion\Nafter the articles were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302510,1304804}I'll take a coffee and a hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304804,1306429}Yes, coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306429,1307223}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307223,1310017}Maya, would you like to go\Nto "Miss White Rose" with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310017,1310768}I have two tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310768,1313103}Oh, that's the one Ms. Ayumi's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313103,1313979}I'd love to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313979,1316023}Then I'll go now and wait for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316023,1317566}Here's the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323906,1325866}Where's Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335918,1336877}Hmm, this is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338963,1341382}Please give it back to me.\NIt's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341382,1342675}Important?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342675,1344218}None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1344218,1346136}It's a purple rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346136,1347428}Please give it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353477,1356938}{\i1}A purple rose that has nothing to do with me…
Comment: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:49.36,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1369368,1369368}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:02.71,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1376625,1382715}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:08.84,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1382715,1388846}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:20.85,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1388846,1400858}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:32.99,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1400858,1412995}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:38.79,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1412995,1418792}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:45.00,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1418792,1425007}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:51.09,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1425007,1431096}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:57.10,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1431096,1437102}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:24:03.15,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1437102,1443150}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:09.15,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1443150,1449156}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
