Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:27.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1462294,1467466}Tsukikage and Ondine participate\Nin Tōkyō prefectural drama contest…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:30.21,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1467466,1470219}…and both are performing\Nthe same play: "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:34.72,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1470219,1474723}The main role of Midori will be played\Nby Kitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi.{NOTE:主役のみどりをやるのは北島マヤと姫川亜弓}
